  <fishName>k__BackingField: Squid
  <fishFact>k__BackingField: 'Squid are jet-propelled, color-changing, ink-squirting
    masters of the open ocean. They have three hearts, blue blood, and eyes remarkably
    similar to human eyes despite evolving completely separately. They''re also among
    the most intelligent invertebrates alive, capable of problem-solving and rapid
    learning. In a pinch, they can sacrifice a tentacle to a predator and simply
    grow it back. '
